Syntax highlighting in Vim

HOW TO INSTALL
--------------

Copy the ftdetect & syntax folders in $HOME/.vim

After doing this, your directory should look like so:

+$HOME
|
|---.vim
     |
     |----syntax
     |      |
     |      |----sial.vim
     |      |----.... (other files)
     |
     |---ftdetect
            |
            |----sial.vim
            |----....(other files)



